{"tid":1542161,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"聖保祿高壓禁罷課","createTime":"2019-09-04T18:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T04:05:57.000Z","uid":266261,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"eb11102767b3166729b6d0f9d666112f6e1a3c18","tid":1542161,"uid":266261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:27:28.000Z","msg":"該校校友陳小姐向《蘋果》表示，有學生向她反映，<span style=\"color: red;\">昨早校門外設置垃圾筒，並有老師看守，要求學生收起或丟棄傳單。但當有同學想收起，則被老師瞪著，示意把傳單丟棄。</span>及後有自稱家長的女士報警，警員對在場校友表示報案人只是感到憂慮，了解後隨即離去。但陳小姐稱有該校教師誣指校友與家長吵罵。<br />\n<br />\n陳小姐與一班校友早前曾用問卷形式調查，全校約四成學生希望罷課。校友8月底聯同關注罷課的學生跟校方開會，但<span style=\"color: red;\">校方態度強硬，不可舉辦公民學堂，又表明學生不可挑戰校規，連任何顏色的口罩及絲帶亦不可佩戴；開學後，校方稱會安排想罷課的學生到老師及社工駐守的特別室，並將通知家長接走學生</span>。陳小姐之後便收到不少同學通知不敢罷課。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190904&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60009126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190904%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60009126&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6ruQPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=41e70ebd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190904%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60009126&h=82db10ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190904&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60009126</a><br />\n<br />\n好惡 傳單都唔俾攞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ad43d408e1bd5de2c49587413526207e9b41cd","tid":1542161,"uid":92836,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:30:35.000Z","msg":"突發 831有個手足走咗！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1542125\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1542125</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4mgWBqJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4mgWBqJ.jpg&h=669e5659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幫手讚同follow<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/反送中的閩僑舊生-104759527572698/\" data-sr-ur